---
---

<section class="py-24 bg-white relative overflow-hidden border-b-8 border-black">
  {/* Diagonal Slash Background */}
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-stripes opacity-5 pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-full h-32 bg-black transform -rotate-3 z-0"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="mb-20 relative">
      <div class="absolute -top-10 -left-10 w-32 h-32 bg-pastel-pink border-4 border-black rounded-full hidden md:block"></div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black uppercase relative z-10 bg-white inline-block border-4 border-black p-3 md:p-4 shadow-hard transform rotate-1">
        TIRED OF{' '}
        <span class="text-pastel-pink bg-black px-2">
          ALGORITHM-DRIVEN
        </span>{' '}
        VIEWING?
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-sm md:text-xl font-bold font-mono bg-pastel-yellow border-4 border-black p-3 md:p-4 inline-block transform -rotate-1 max-w-2xl shadow-hard">
        &gt; DETECTED: Modern streaming is broken.
        <br />
        &gt; SOLUTION: Manual override required.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      {/* Problem 1: Algorithm Overlord */}
      <div class="relative p-6 border-4 border-black shadow-hard hover:shadow-hard-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-200 bg-pastel-mint rotate-1">
        <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 bg-black text-white font-mono text-xs p-1 border-2 border-white">
          ERR_001
        </div>
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white border-4 border-black flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-hard-sm">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="3">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight border-b-4 border-black pb-2 inline-block">
          Algorithm Overlord
        </h3>
        <p class="font-bold text-sm leading-relaxed mt-2">
          Streaming services decide what you watch based on 'engagement', not your actual interests. Time to reject the feed.
        </p>
        <div class="absolute bottom-2 right-2 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-2 right-5 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-5 right-2 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
      </div>

      {/* Problem 2: The Doom Scroll */}
      <div class="relative p-6 border-4 border-black shadow-hard hover:shadow-hard-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-200 bg-pastel-pink -rotate-1">
        <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 bg-black text-white font-mono text-xs p-1 border-2 border-white">
          ERR_002
        </div>
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white border-4 border-black flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-hard-sm">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="3">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight border-b-4 border-black pb-2 inline-block">
          The Doom Scroll
        </h3>
        <p class="font-bold text-sm leading-relaxed mt-2">
          Spending 45 minutes looking for something to watch, only to fall asleep 10 minutes in. System failure.
        </p>
        <div class="absolute bottom-2 right-2 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-2 right-5 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-5 right-2 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
      </div>

      {/* Problem 3: Fragmented Library */}
      <div class="relative p-6 border-4 border-black shadow-hard hover:shadow-hard-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-200 bg-pastel-blue rotate-1">
        <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 bg-black text-white font-mono text-xs p-1 border-2 border-white">
          ERR_003
        </div>
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white border-4 border-black flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-hard-sm">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="3">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight border-b-4 border-black pb-2 inline-block">
          Fragmented Library
        </h3>
        <p class="font-bold text-sm leading-relaxed mt-2">
          Your watchlist is scattered across 7 different apps, notes, and mental reminders. Database corrupted.
        </p>
        <div class="absolute bottom-2 right-2 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-2 right-5 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-5 right-2 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
      </div>

      {/* Problem 4: Never Finishing */}
      <div class="relative p-6 border-4 border-black shadow-hard hover:shadow-hard-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-200 bg-pastel-yellow -rotate-1">
        <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 bg-black text-white font-mono text-xs p-1 border-2 border-white">
          ERR_004
        </div>
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white border-4 border-black flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-hard-sm">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="3">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 14l2-2m0 0l2-2m-2 2l-2-2m2 2l2 2m7-2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight border-b-4 border-black pb-2 inline-block">
          Never Finishing
        </h3>
        <p class="font-bold text-sm leading-relaxed mt-2">
          Starting great shows but forgetting to come back to them when life gets busy. Progress halted.
        </p>
        <div class="absolute bottom-2 right-2 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-2 right-5 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-5 right-2 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
      </div>

      {/* Problem 5: Decision Fatigue */}
      <div class="relative p-6 border-4 border-black shadow-hard hover:shadow-hard-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-200 bg-pastel-purple rotate-1">
        <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 bg-black text-white font-mono text-xs p-1 border-2 border-white">
          ERR_005
        </div>
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white border-4 border-black flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-hard-sm">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="3">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight border-b-4 border-black pb-2 inline-block">
          Decision Fatigue
        </h3>
        <p class="font-bold text-sm leading-relaxed mt-2">
          After a long day of making choices, deciding what to watch feels like work. CPU overload.
        </p>
        <div class="absolute bottom-2 right-2 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-2 right-5 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-5 right-2 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
      </div>

      {/* Problem 6: Social Noise */}
      <div class="relative p-6 border-4 border-black shadow-hard hover:shadow-hard-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-200 bg-pastel-orange -rotate-1">
        <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 bg-black text-white font-mono text-xs p-1 border-2 border-white">
          ERR_006
        </div>
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white border-4 border-black flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-hard-sm">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="3">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.875 18.825A10.05 10.05 0 0112 19c-4.478 0-8.268-2.943-9.543-7a9.97 9.97 0 011.563-3.029m5.858.908a3 3 0 114.243 4.243M9.878 9.878l4.242 4.242M9.88 9.88l-3.29-3.29m7.532 7.532l3.29 3.29M3 3l3.59 3.59m0 0A9.953 9.953 0 0112 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.543 7a10.025 10.025 0 01-4.132 5.411m0 0L21 21" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight border-b-4 border-black pb-2 inline-block">
          Social Noise
        </h3>
        <p class="font-bold text-sm leading-relaxed mt-2">
          Spoilers, hot takes, and social pressure distracting you from just enjoying the show. Signal interference.
        </p>
        <div class="absolute bottom-2 right-2 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-2 right-5 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-5 right-2 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .shadow-hard-xl {
    box-shadow: 12px 12px 0 0 black;
  }
</style>
